<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10516850>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Hydrosmecta koreana sp. nov. A: labrum (dorsal view); B: epipharynx (ventral view); C: right mandible (dorsal view); D: left mandible (ventral view); E: left maxilla (ventral view); F: labium and mentum (ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10516850/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10516852>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Hydrosmecta koreana sp. nov. A: head (ventral view); B: antenna; C: pronotum (dorsal view); D: prosternum (ventral view); E: metanotum (dorsal view); F: meso- and metaventrites (ventral view); G: scutellum (dorsal view); H: elytron (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10516852/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10516854>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Hydrosmecta koreana sp. nov. A: abdominal tergites VI and VII (dorsal view); B: microsculpture of male abdominal tergite VIII (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10516854/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10516856>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Hydrosmecta koreana sp. nov. A: male abdominal tergite VIII (dorsal view); B: male abdominal sternite VIII (ventral view); C: female abdominal tergite VIII (dorsal view); D: female abdominal sternite VIII (ventral view); E: median lobe of aedeagus (lateral view); F: median lobe of aedeagus (ventral view); G: paramere (lateral view); H: spermatheca. Scales = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10516856/files/figure.png" ;
